channel.title: Kicked me out of my own server!
channel.description: Can somebody help me? I'm using the only best source, and it kicked me out of my server and my name was "Admin Nate" before it lagged me out, then wouldn't let me in, it said come back with a name without symbols. I don't exactly want to change my name to anything other then that. Could somebody tell me how to make it so it doesn't do that?
